=== Spec Example 2.18. Multi-line Flow Scalars
--- from: http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2761268
--- tags: spec scalar

--- in-yaml
plain:
  This unquoted scalar
  spans many lines.

quoted: "So does this
  quoted scalar.\n"

--- in-json
{
  "plain": "This unquoted scalar spans many lines.",
  "quoted": "So does this quoted scalar.\n"
}

--- out-yaml
plain: This unquoted scalar spans many lines.
quoted: "So does this quoted scalar.\n"

